---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Complaints Procedure"
  description="Read our complaints procedure to understand how Golden Pathway handles client feedback and resolves issues in accordance with UK regulations."
>
  <div class="space-y-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Complaints Procedure</h1>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-main leading-relaxed">
        Golden Pathway ("we", "us", or "our") is committed to providing a high
        standard of information and service. If you are dissatisfied with any
        aspect of our website or the information provided, you have the right to
        make a complaint. This procedure outlines how you can make a complaint
        and how we will handle it, in accordance with UK law.
      </p>

      <h2 class="pt-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-text-main">
        How to Make a Complaint
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-main leading-relaxed">
        If you wish to make a complaint, please contact us by email at <a
          href="mailto:info@goldenpathway.co.uk"
          class="underline">info@goldenpathway.co.uk</a
        > with the following details:
      </p>
      <ul
        class="list-disc pl-6 text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-main leading-relaxed"
      >
        <li>Your name and contact details</li>
        <li>A clear description of your complaint</li>
        <li>Any relevant supporting information or evidence</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="pt-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-text-main">
        What Happens Next
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-main leading-relaxed">
        We will acknowledge receipt of your complaint within 5 working days. We
        aim to investigate and respond to all complaints within 20 working days.
        If we need more time, we will let you know and provide an estimated
        timescale.
      </p>

      <h2 class="pt-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-text-main">Our Commitment</h2>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-main leading-relaxed">
        We will treat your complaint seriously, fairly, and confidentially. We
        will investigate the issues raised and take appropriate action where
        necessary. We will keep you informed throughout the process and provide
        a clear explanation of our findings and any actions taken.
      </p>

      <h2 class="pt-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-text-main">
        If You Are Not Satisfied
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-main leading-relaxed">
        If you are not satisfied with our response, you may request a review of
        your complaint. We will conduct a further review and provide a final
        response. If you remain dissatisfied, you may seek independent advice or
        contact the relevant regulatory body in the UK.
      </p>

      <h2 class="pt-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-text-main">Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-main leading-relaxed">
        For all complaints and related correspondence, please contact us at <a
          href="mailto:info@goldenpathway.co.uk"
          class="underline">info@goldenpathway.co.uk</a
        >.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
